                "invention-title": [
                    "Device and method for improving heat efficiency of heating furnace, protecting environment and reducing emission",
                    "一种提高加热炉热效率和环保减排的装置及方法"
                ]
            },
            "abstract": [
                {
                    "p": "According to the device and method for improving the heat efficiency of the heating furnace and achieving environmental protection and emission reduction, by combining a green electricity water electrolysis hydrogen production process, the problems that an existing heating furnace is low in heat efficiency, and meanwhile a large number of pollutants and greenhouse gases are discharged are effectively solved, resource recycling is achieved, and the environmental protection and emission reduction effects are achieved. The increasing environmental protection and double-carbon requirements at the present stage are met."
                },
                {
                    "p": "本发明提供了一种提高加热炉热效率和环保减排的装置及方法，通过结合绿电电解水制氢工艺，有效解决了目前加热炉热效率较低，同时造成大量污染物及温室气体排放的问题，并形成资源循环利用，满足现阶段日益提高的环保及“双碳”要求。"
                }
            ]
